OL,3,CMan shot wife and dog before turning
OL,4,Cgun on himself, inquest heard
OL,6,FA married couple were found dead in
OL,7,Ftheir home by their daughter after a
OL,8,Fmurder-suicide, an inquest has heard.
OL,10,FStephen Jefferies, 74, shot his wife
OL,11,FChristine, 72, and their dog, May, at
OL,12,Fthe family home in the Trowbridge area
OL,13,Fof Cardiff on October 5 last year.
OL,15,FThe couple were found by their
OL,16,Fdaughter Martine Stecker who visited
OL,17,Fthe house to check on her parents
OL,18,Ffollowing a call from a concerned
OL,19,Fneighbour.
