OL,3,CMan shot wife and dog before turning
OL,4,Cgun on himself, inquest heard
OL,6,FInside, she discovered the bodies of
OL,7,Fher parents in the bedroom.
OL,9,FAn inquest at Pontypridd Coroner's
OL,10,FCourt concluded Mr Jefferies had
OL,11,Fkilled his wife and dog, before
OL,12,Fturning the gun on himself.
OL,14,FThe inquest heard Mr Jefferies had a
OL,15,Fhistory of depression and the couple
OL,16,Fwere in #35,000 of debt at the time of
OL,17,Fthe incident.
OL,19,F"I never had an inkling they had money
OL,20,Fissues at all," Ms Stecker said.
