OL,6,F"I think (my father) had the world on
OL,7,Fhis shoulders but never showed
OL,8,Fanything.
OL,10,F"I don't think my mother was involved
OL,11,Fin any of this, I think her life was
OL,12,Ftaken away from her."
OL,14,FThe couple were married in 1970 and
OL,15,Fhad two children, Martine and her
OL,16,Fbrother Gethin.
OL,18,FMs Stecker said they had a good
OL,19,Fchildhood but she was aware her father
OL,20,Fhad struggled with his mental health
OL,21,Fin recent years.
