OL,3,CMan shot wife and dog before turning
OL,4,Cgun on himself, inquest heard
OL,6,FShe said: "He lost his sister,
OL,7,Fsomething happened in his workplace
OL,8,Fwhere he was being bullied.
OL,10,F"I had no concerns that he really had
OL,11,Fdepression.
OL,13,F"What I did find strange is when he
OL,14,Fkept going on about the wills, wanting
OL,15,Fto change it, I thought that was
OL,16,Fstrange at the time," she added.
OL,18,F"I dismissed it because I just didn't
OL,19,Funderstand why he wanted to change it
OL,20,Fall of a sudden after all these years."
