OL,3,CMan shot wife and dog before turning
OL,4,Cgun on himself, inquest heard
OL,6,FThe court heard Mrs Jefferies had
OL,7,Fsuffered with chronic pain and took
OL,8,Fmedication to treat this.
OL,10,FHowever, she maintained an active
OL,11,Fsocial life and met her daughter every
OL,12,FSaturday.
OL,14,F"We'd go to the garden centre, we'd go
OL,15,Ffor coffee or we'd go shopping, just a
OL,16,Fmother and daughter thing," Ms Stecker
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FWhen Ms Stecker arrived at the house
OL,20,Fon October 5, she found the curtains
OL,21,Fdrawn and the key in the door.
