OL,3,CMan shot wife and dog before turning
OL,4,Cgun on himself, inquest heard
OL,6,F"I really didn't have that much
OL,7,Fconcern at all... I don't think it
OL,8,Freally hit me straight away," she said.
OL,10,FMs Stecker discovered the body of the
OL,11,Ffamily dog before finding her mother
OL,12,Flying in bed.
OL,14,FShe said: "I don't even know if I saw
OL,15,Fmy dad... I just knew my mother wasn't
OL,16,Fwith us any more.
OL,18,F"I was quite calm, there was no
OL,19,Fhysteria, no scream."
