OL,3,CMan shot wife and dog before turning
OL,4,Cgun on himself, inquest heard
OL,6,FThe court heard Mr Jefferies owned
OL,7,Fseveral guns as he used to go clay
OL,8,Fpigeon and pheasant shooting.
OL,10,FThe couple were found to owe some
OL,11,F#35,000 after their deaths, though it
OL,12,Fis not clear how they acquired the
OL,13,Fdebt.
OL,15,FArea coroner Patricia Morgan concluded
OL,16,Fthe couple both died from gunshot
OL,17,Fwounds to the head.
OL,19,FShe ruled Mrs Jefferies' death was an
OL,20,Funlawful killing while Mr Jefferies'
OL,21,Fcause of death was suicide.
