OL,3,CMan shot wife and dog before turning
OL,4,Cgun on himself, inquest heard
OL,6,FShe said: "It is likely that Mrs
OL,7,FJefferies was shot by her husband
OL,8,Fbefore he went on to shoot the family
OL,9,Fdog and then himself.
OL,11,F"Her husband had some historical
OL,12,Fdepression and was likely suffering
OL,13,Fwith a deterioration in his mental
OL,14,Fhealth."
OL,16,F"They had some financial debts but it
OL,17,Fis not known to what extent this had
OL,18,Fcaused them stress or worry," she
OL,19,Fadded.
